{"tid":1188330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]人氣日韓女團7月襲港！！","createTime":"2019-06-06T07:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T09:16:44.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b377c32a0f0717b8e3d8d4efb12acc30f0891ec","tid":1188330,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190606140336\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190606140336&h=cb00b9de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190606140336\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190606140336&h=931e10f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190606/photo/bkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190606140336\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190606134229272-0606_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190606140336&h=a2062781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本AV女優三上悠亞2015年以SKE48成員身份加入藝能界，一直心醉韓國K-pop的她，去年3月聯同另外兩名AV女優成員櫻萌子和松田美子組成Honey Popcorn。可是出道未夠一年，松田美子去年12月宣布離隊，令到不少粉絲擔心Honey Popcorn會就此解散。好消息宣布，三上和櫻萌子已找到新成員加入，而且一加就三個。 <br />\n<br />\n至於新成員的神秘真面目，5月31日至6月14日這段期間，會每星期逐個揭開面罩，粉絲可以在Honey Popcorn的官方IG見到。而新成員登場後，三上將與她們來港同粉絲見面，定7月27日在西港城舉行《Honey Popcorn Fan Meeting In Hong Kong 2019》見面會，5位成員會同大家大玩遊戲，購票的粉絲更獲幸運福袋。"},{"pid":"a7e80f7bc7e7fa9819d40fdebc04d3c89118afa9","tid":1188330,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"搞感謝祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485aaecbb27c8525c7ceb56ac24e4ddd6d7f81cd","tid":1188330,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"三上 &amp; Dancers"},{"pid":"f8517c3563923d9da6ec7ca18ba71bd36e86b3fc","tid":1188330,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"1380 680<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13665bd6f5a5a3e7447560b4b5e0c2504fa7b14","tid":1188330,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"已經放左張IZONE VIP出去轉睇三上了.."},{"pid":"e76a87f1b54d83e47018780edfe640c62ca9ba10","tid":1188330,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"屌以為izone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a59a393a7a83dcf810fd560758836bd22b5bc23","tid":1188330,"uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c13665bd6f5a5a3e7447560b4b5e0c2504fa7b14","tid":1188330,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"已經放左張IZONE VIP出去轉睇三上了.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"IZONE最多都係摸下手<br />\n哩隊分分鐘可以揸波..."},{"pid":"6780dd59724fb9f56e7c00db3bb98653877efba6","tid":1188330,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a59a393a7a83dcf810fd560758836bd22b5bc23","tid":1188330,"uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c13665bd6f5a5a3e7447560b4b5e0c2504fa7b14","tid":1188330,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"已經放左張IZONE VIP出去轉睇三上了.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"IZONE最多都係摸下手<br />\n哩隊分分鐘可以揸波..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"